OL,4,Ctheatre capacity and protect planned
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FNottingham University Hospitals NHS
OL,8,FTrust has committed to protecting
OL,9,Fplanned care this winter to prevent
OL,10,Fpressures from seasonal illnesses
OL,11,Fhaving an impact on wait times.
OL,13,FThis year, the trust started planning
OL,14,Ffor winter earlier than ever to ensure
OL,15,Felective procedures could continue
OL,16,Fthroughout the winter months.
