OL,4,Ctheatre capacity and protect planned
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FThe plan includes initiatives such as
OL,8,Fthe short-stay hip and knee
OL,9,Freplacement pathway, high-intensity
OL,10,Ftheatre lists and dual operating
OL,11,Ftheatres to maximise capacity and
OL,12,Fbenefit patients.
OL,14,FLast month elective orthopaedic
OL,15,Factivity at the trust was at 124% of
OL,16,Fpre-Covid activity, compared with
OL,17,FNovember 2019.
