OL,7,FJennifer Beaumont, deputy chief
OL,8,Foperating officer at the trust said:
OL,9,F"One of our top priorities this winter
OL,10,Fis to continue planned care and
OL,11,Fprocedures as much as possible.
OL,13,F"Winter is an extremely busy time for
OL,14,Fthe NHS however it is a priority for
OL,15,Fus to maximise our theatre and
OL,16,Foutpatient capacity to continue to
OL,17,Freduce waiting lists and improve
OL,18,Fpatient experience.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@AOU
