OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F371A1734440347
OL,3,CNottingham hospitals to maximise
OL,4,Ctheatre capacity and protect planned
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"In previous years we have had to
OL,8,Freduce elective operating capacity
OL,9,Fover winter due to bed pressures from
OL,10,Femergency admissions.
OL,12,F"This year we have planned additional
OL,13,Fbed capacity so we can protect planned
OL,14,Fcare to ensure procedures can continue.
OL,16,F"Our teams have worked incredibly hard
OL,17,Fto significantly reduce 65-week waits
OL,18,FTrust wide and we are still on track
OL,19,Fto eliminate almost all orthopaedics
OL,20,F52-week waits by the end of March.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
