OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"We know how important it is to our
OL,8,Fpatients to continue with planned care
OL,9,Fand reduce waiting lists as quickly
OL,10,Fand safely as possible."
OL,12,FLast year, the trust introduced a
OL,13,Fshort-stay hip and knee replacement
OL,14,Fpathway aimed at discharging patients
OL,15,Fon the same day as their surgery.
OL,17,FIn the first six months of the
OL,18,Fpathway, 58% of patients were
OL,19,Fdischarged from hospital within 24
OL,20,Fhours of surgery, compared to only 10%
OL,21,Fbefore it was introduced.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@XO]
