OL,7,FThe average length of stay following a
OL,8,Fhip or knee replacement has now
OL,9,Freduced by over two days allowing us
OL,10,Fto increase operating capacity, reduce
OL,11,Fwaiting lists and free up beds for
OL,12,Fother patients.
OL,14,FBenjamin Bloch, consultant orthopaedic
OL,15,Fsurgeon, said: "The pathway continues
OL,16,Fto be a real success and is helping us
OL,17,Fmaximise theatre capacity and continue
OL,18,Fwith elective procedures as we head
OL,19,Finto winter.
OL,26,@wD@POU
