OL,3,CNottingham hospitals to maximise
OL,4,Ctheatre capacity and protect planned
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"We first introduced the pathway to
OL,8,Ftry to get patients out of hospital
OL,9,Fmuch more quickly because the best
OL,10,Fplace to recover is at home.
OL,12,F"It's great that we have also improved
OL,13,Foperating capacity helping us to
OL,14,Freduce waiting lists and free up
OL,15,Fhospital beds for other patients who
OL,16,Fneed them.
OL,18,F"If we can use our resources more
OL,19,Fefficiently and get more patients
OL,20,Fseen, then that can only be a good
OL,21,Fthing."
